      "role": "user",
      "content": "everyone keeps telling me i just need to see a psych or take some pills to \"fix\" my brain but it feels like such a lie. like they just want to numb me so i stop being a problem for society. is there actually any truth to what they say or is it all just a way to keep us controlled and quiet?",
